Message: Ekkuvagaa contractives vadadam arogyaaniki mamchidi kaadu. Imduvalla kadupulo neppichati noppinausea baruvu peragadamtalanoppi  vamti samasyalu eduravutayi.
Evarikaina HIV infection sokite vaariki saraina  vaidyam jaragakapote sadharanamgaa  ee vyadhi sokina dadapou 10 ellalo AIDS  vachhe avakasam vumtumdi..

Missionary position lo sex jarapadam valana conception ayyemduku avalasalunnayi kaabatti idi uttamamainadi.  Sperm yoniloniki ati sameepamga vellagaladu.

Garbhavati mahilaki HIV infection vumte aame dwara biddaku  garbham dharimchi vunna samayamlo kaani prasava samayamlo ee infection vachche pramadam vumtumdi.
HIV positive mahila HIV nagative purushudu biddaki HIV sokakumda vumdadaani artificial insemination paddhatini upayogimchavachchunu.
Sex valla energy levels perugutaayani amdariki telusu.  Tarachuga sex lo paalgonadam mamchidi.  Imduvalla stress levels taggadame kakumda baruvu kuda taggutaaru.
Oral sex jaruputunna samayamlo skalamainappudu veeryam notilono sareeram meedo padutumdi.  Kaabatti deenivalla avamchita garbham vastumdanna bhayam vumdadu..
HIV infection raakumda vumdadaaniki condoms vadadam vuttamamaina paddhati.  Garbha nirodhaka maatralu vadadam kamte ivi vadadam mamchidi.
Niyamitamgaa Vitamin B-Complex anaga B1 numchi  B5  mariyu B-12 vadadam valla sex patla korika perugutumdi.  Idi rakta prasarananu kuda vruddhi chestumdi.
Okari kamte ekkuvamamdito oral sexlo paalgonnavaariki  STD anagaa sexually transmitted diseases vachche avakasam chaala ekkuvagaa vumtumdi.
Pakkapakkane padukune amga pravesam jarapadam valana eddaripaina takkuva stress padutumdi.  Mukhyamgaa vubakaayam vunnavarikidi chaala upayogamgaa vumtumdi.
Kevalam kallu moosukuni partner ni chumbimchadam valana udrekam pomdagalagadame kaakumda ekkuva aanamdam kuda  pomde avakaasam ekkuvavutumdi.
Sex therapistula amchana prakaram sex lo anamdaanni ekkuvagaa pomdina mahilalu tama sareeram lotupatlani ekkuvaga pattimchukoru.
Herpes vunna vyaktule churuggaa virus vyapimpajestaarani emi ledu.  Amduke condom ellappudu upayogimchadam alavaatugaa maaraali.
Laimgika pratispamdana medaduloni neurotransmitters dwara prarambhamavutumdi.  Medadu kanaalanu raktaprasarananu pemchadam dwara marmavayavaalato samdhistayi.
Antidepressants mamdulu vadite mood bagunnatlu  anipimchinappatiki avi medaduloni neurotransmitters balance ni paadu chesi sex ki srushtistayi.
HIV infection vachchinappudu sareera kanaalu balaheenamayi immune system sarigga pani cheyyalekapotumdi.   Amduvalla AIDS baarina padataaru.
Sthreelu tamato snehamgaa vunna vyaktulane ishtapadataarani parisodhanalo telimdi.  Adhikaarapoorvakamgaa pravartimche magavaaramte vaallaki istham vumdadu.
Teenage lo vunnavaarito talidamdruolu snehapooritamgaa vyavaharimchali. Appude vaallu dhairyamgaa tama samasyalanu vaallaki cheppukogalugutaaru.
Sthree  pushudito tana sambhamdaanni tarachugaa bereeju vesukuni choosukumtoo vumtumdi.  Adi purushudu emta akarshaneeyamgaa vunnadane daanimeeda  vumtumdi.
Pillalaki veelainamta twaragaa sareera avayavaala perlu parichayam cheyyadame kaakumdaa marmavayavaala gurimchi cheppadaaniki siggu padakudadu.
Latex leda polyurethane to tayaaraina male condom ayinaa female condom ayinaa -  ee okka technology ye sexual ga HIV raakumdaa kaapaadutumdi.
Rajo nivrutti samayamlo jarige harmonal changes valana yoni kumchimchukupotumdi.  Amte kaakumdaa yonimargam pottigaa ayyi yoni godalu mamdamgaa avutaayi.
Appudappudu sexki dooramgaa vumdadam avasaram kuda. Oka clublo cheradamo gymlo vyayamam cheyyadamo vamtivi chesete sex meeda numdi drushti maralutumdi.
Dating chestunnapudusabhyata samskaralanu paatimchadam gurtumchukomdi.  Tarachugaa aameni prasamsimchamdi.  Chinna vushayaale sakhyataki daari teestaayi.
Yogabhyasam cheyyadam mimmalni adhika laimgika vaamchalaku dooramgaa vumchutumdi. Mamchi bhojanapu alavaatlu korikalanu adupulo vumchukovadaniki sahayapadatayi.
Sex korikalanu adupulo vumchukovalanukumte pornography choodadam leda itara stimulations ki dooramgaa vumdadam alavatu chesukovali
Sambhogam samyamlo noppi kalagadam sadhaaranamgaa jarugutune vumtumdi. Ayite gynaecologist ni okasari sampradimchadam annividhaala mamchidi.
